API list:

Best Buy API - Get prices for old and new products at Best Buy
link: https://bbyopen.com/documentation/stores-api

Ebay Shopping API - Get prices and info on products on eBay
link: http://developer.ebay.com/Devzone/shopping/docs/CallRef/index.html

Key Ring API - Users sign in and can recieve other rewards in their Key Ring account
link: http://keyringapp.com/about

Foursquare API - Users sign/check in and can get other discounts from shopping
link: https://developer.foursquare.com/docs/



Maybe list:

Celery - Pre-pay for products